Let’s talk

Sojitz cuts time to market with multi-site management tools

INTRODUCTION

Sojitz is a general trading company that has been in operation for more than 150 years, with multiple subsidiaries in Japan and around the globe. One area the company specializes in is bringing large automotive brands to the Japanese market.

ACCELERATED WEB CREATION

60% reduction in time to market

NO-CODE CAPABILITIES

Reduced dependency on dev team

FULL-STACK DEV ENVIRONMENT

Seamless integration with existing systems

INTUITIVE CMS

More efficient content management

CLIENT SUCCESS STORY

Sojitz was rapidly expanding its dealership network with brands including BMW, Volvo, and Maserati. Plus, the company became the exclusive importer and seller for BYD, the largest electric vehicle brand in Japan.

​

To support this expansion, the Sojitz team needed to build custom sites—fast. This proved difficult to achieve with limited developer resources. Thanks to Wix Studio for enterprise, the team was able to simplify complex workflows and step up website creation—significantly.

Sojitz
